headline: Stock Market Today: Dow Rallies, S&P 500 And Nasdaq Make History; Nvidia, Palantir Both Do This
summary: The Dow Jones Industrial Average and other major indexes ended Tuesday with significant gains of more than 1% each, as investors anticipate upcoming rate cuts following July inflation numbers.  Both Palantir Technologies and Nvidia made new highs on the stock market today.  The Dow finished up 1.1%, or 483 points, and more than recovered Monday's 200-point drop.
